%% MLflow Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.2/mlflow.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as ML Client (SDK)
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAuth as kubernetes-auth Plugin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant LLM as LLM Provider API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking (Create Run)
    Client->>Proxy: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP/5000)<br/>x-remote-user, x-remote-groups headers
    MLflow->>K8sAuth: Authorize request
    K8sAuth->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>resource: experiments<br/>verb: create
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAuth: Allowed
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run record<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Run created
    MLflow->>S3: PUT artifact<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>MLflow: Upload complete
    MLflow-->>Proxy: 200 OK (run_id)
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Workspace Resolution
    Client->>MLflow: GET /api/3.0/mlflow/workspaces<br/>X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE header
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: List namespaces (cached watch)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Namespace list
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: Watch MLflowConfig CRDs (cached)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: MLflowConfig resources
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: GET Secret mlflow-artifact-connection<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Artifact root override
    MLflow-->>Client: Workspace details

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 3: AI Gateway LLM Invocation
    Client->>MLflow: POST /gateway/{endpoint}/mlflow/invocations<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    MLflow->>K8sAuth: Authorize request
    K8sAuth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>resource: gatewayendpoints/use
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAuth: Allowed
    MLflow->>PG: Load endpoint + model definition<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Config + encrypted API key
    MLflow->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API Key (decrypted)
    LLM-->>MLflow: LLM Response
    MLflow-->>Client: Gateway Response

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 4: OTLP Trace Ingestion
    Client->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    MLflow->>K8sAuth: Authorize (experiments permission)
    K8sAuth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAuth: Allowed
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT trace spans<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Stored
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK
